                    </div>
                    <span style="background: #f2f2f7; color: #1d1d1f; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">2017 - 2021</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="position: relative; margin-bottom: 45px; padding-left: 30px;">
                <div style="position: absolute; left: -36px; top: 5px; width: 14px; height: 14px; background: #fff; border: 3px solid #007aff; border-radius: 50%; z-index: 2;"></div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;">
                    <div>
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #86868b; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;">Bursa Uludağ Üniversitesi</span>
